.IX Subsection "new"
.PP
.Vb 1
\&  my $stack = autodie::Scope::GuardStack\->new;
.Ve
.PP
Creates a new \f(CW\*(C`autodie::Scope::GuardStack\*(C'\fR.  The stack is initially
